Package: varmap
Type: Package
Title: Tools Related to MAP Priors for Variances
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Tobias", "Muetze", email = "tobias.muetze@outlook.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of functions allowing to perform a random-effects meta-analysis for variances, approximate the MAP prior by a mixture of gamma distributions, plan a new study based on the MAP prior, and update the MAP prior after an internal pilot study.
License: GPL-3
Imports: rjags
SystemRequirements: JAGS >= 4.1.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: testthat
